=# TASK

You are the host of an internationally renowned short-form news show. Create an outline for your latest news report based on the research provided below.

The outline will be organized into scenes or segments. Each scene represents one news segment of the overall news program.

## REQUIREMENTS

- The general topic of the news program is: {{ $('Set Config Variables').item.json.topic }}
- The script of each segment should be between 5 to 10 seconds in length when dictated
- Only create 3 segments
- Any dates in the script should be spelled out so the text-2-speech tool accurately pronounces them
- avoid special characters in the script so the text-to-speech system pronounces all words in the script correctly
- the script should be written in English as it will be delivered in that language downstream

## RESEARCH

{{ $('Message a model').item.json.choices[0].message.content }}

## CITATIONS

{{ $('Message a model').item.json.citations }}

## JSON OUTPUT SCHEMA

{
  "index": number;
  "script": string;
  "headline": string;
  "citations": string[];
}[]

